-- MOVES-ING Investment hires Avoca managers for convertible bond team
-- 
-- Tue Dec 09, 2014 02:58PM EST
-- None



Dec 9 (Reuters) - ING Investment Management hired Tarek Saber as investment team manager and Jasper van Ingen as a senior portfolio manager to its convertible bond markets team.

Saber and van Ingen join from Avoca Convertible Select Global Fund, where they were managers.